Render a summary table from wcvp_summary

Source: R/wcvp_summary.r
wcvp_summary_gt.Rd

Render a summary table from wcvp_summary

wcvp_summary_gt(x)

Arguments

x

List.

Value

gt table

Examples

ferns <- wcvp_summary("Ferns", "higher", get_wgsrpd3_codes("New Zealand"), grouping.var="family")
#> ℹ Matches to input geography found at Country (Gallagher) and Region (Level 2)
#> ℹ Aggregating occurrence types across input areas - see `?wcvp_summary()` for details.
wcvp_summary_gt(ferns)
